"""
PURPOSE: Store network-based features from relationship graphs
FORMAT: Parquet with adjacency information
CONTENTS:
- node_id: Entity identifier (customer/merchant/device)
- node_type: Type of entity
- degree_centrality: Number of connections
- betweenness_centrality: Bridge between communities
- community_id: Detected fraud ring identifier
- clustering_coefficient: How connected neighbors are
- pagerank: PageRank score in transaction network
- suspicious_connections: Count of risky connections
- shared_devices: Number of customers sharing device
- shared_ips: Number of customers sharing IP
- fraud_propagation_score: Risk from connected entities
"""